name: NSPrintInfo.AttributeKey
desc: Constants that specify print job attributes.

items.name: static let paperName: NSPrintInfo.AttributeKey
items.desc: An NSString object containing the paper name.

items.name: static let paperSize: NSPrintInfo.AttributeKey
items.desc: An NSSize value specifying the height and width of paper in points.

items.name: static let orientation: NSPrintInfo.AttributeKey
items.desc: An NSNumber object containing an NSPrintingOrientation.

items.name: static let scalingFactor: NSPrintInfo.AttributeKey
items.desc: Scale factor percentage before pagination.

items.name: static let leftMargin: NSPrintInfo.AttributeKey
items.desc: NSNumber, containing a floating-point value that specifies the left margin, in points.

items.name: static let rightMargin: NSPrintInfo.AttributeKey
items.desc: NSNumber, containing a floating-point value that specifies the right margin, in points.

items.name: static let topMargin: NSPrintInfo.AttributeKey
items.desc: NSNumber, containing a floating-point value that specifies the top margin, in points.

items.name: static let bottomMargin: NSPrintInfo.AttributeKey
items.desc: NSNumber, containing a floating-point value that specifies the bottom margin, in points.

items.name: static let horizontallyCentered: NSPrintInfo.AttributeKey
items.desc: NSNumber, containing a Boolean value that is true if pages are centered horizontally.

items.name: static let verticallyCentered: NSPrintInfo.AttributeKey
items.desc: NSNumber, containing a Boolean value that is true if pages are centered vertically.

items.name: static let horizontalPagination: NSPrintInfo.AttributeKey
items.desc: NSNumber, containing a NSPrintingPaginationMode value.

items.name: static let verticalPagination: NSPrintInfo.AttributeKey
items.desc: NSNumber, containing a NSPrintingPaginationMode value.

items.name: static let allPages: NSPrintInfo.AttributeKey
items.desc: An NSNumber object containing a Boolean value—if true, includes all pages in output.

items.name: static let copies: NSPrintInfo.AttributeKey
items.desc: An NSNumber object containing an integer—the number of copies to spool.

items.name: static let detailedErrorReporting: NSPrintInfo.AttributeKey
items.desc: An NSNumber object containing a Boolean value—if true, produce detailed reports when an error occurs.

items.name: static let faxNumber: NSPrintInfo.AttributeKey
items.desc: An NSString object that specifies a fax number.

items.name: static let firstPage: NSPrintInfo.AttributeKey
items.desc: An NSNumber object containing an integer value that specifies the first page in the print job.

items.name: static let headerAndFooter: NSPrintInfo.AttributeKey
items.desc: An NSNumber object containing a Boolean value—if true, a standard header and footer are added outside the margins of each page.

items.name: static let jobDisposition: NSPrintInfo.AttributeKey
items.desc: An NSString object that specifies the job disposition.

items.name: static let jobSavingFileNameExtensionHidden: NSPrintInfo.AttributeKey
items.desc: A Boolean NSNumber indicating whether the job’s file name extension should be hidden when the jobDisposition is save. The default is false.

items.name: static let jobSavingURL: NSPrintInfo.AttributeKey
items.desc: An NSURL containing the location to which the job file will be saved when the jobDisposition is save.

items.name: static let lastPage: NSPrintInfo.AttributeKey
items.desc: An NSNumber object containing an integer value that specifies the last page in the print job.

items.name: static let mustCollate: NSPrintInfo.AttributeKey
items.desc: An NSNumber object containing a Boolean value—if true, collates output.

items.name: static let pagesAcross: NSPrintInfo.AttributeKey
items.desc: An NSNumber object that specifies the number of logical pages to be tiled horizontally on a physical sheet of paper.

items.name: static let pagesDown: NSPrintInfo.AttributeKey
items.desc: An NSNumber object that specifies the number of logical pages to be tiled vertically on a physical sheet of paper.

items.name: static let printer: NSPrintInfo.AttributeKey
items.desc: An NSPrinter object—the printer to use.

items.name: static let printerName: NSPrintInfo.AttributeKey
items.desc: An NSString object that specifies the name of a printer.

items.name: static let reversePageOrder: NSPrintInfo.AttributeKey
items.desc: An NSNumber object containing a Boolean value—if true, prints first page last.

items.name: static let selectionOnly: NSPrintInfo.AttributeKey
items.desc: An NSNumber object containing a Boolean value—if true only the current selection is printed.

items.name: static let time: NSPrintInfo.AttributeKey
items.desc: An NSDate object that specifies the time at which printing should begin.

items.name: init(String)
items.desc: Creates a print job attribute key.

items.name: init(rawValue: String)
items.desc: Creates a new instance with the specified raw value.
